Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:32.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}人类动物园,我不敢相信居然还存在\N{\fnArial\fs48}The Human Zoo. I can't believe it still exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:34.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸肯定在里面\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad's got to be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:36.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们只要找到他并将他救出来\N{\fnArial\fs48}We just have to find him and bust him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.71,0:00:46.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那些宝石人\N{\fnArial\fs48}Those Gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:48.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}紫晶守卫\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:50.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}是啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:51.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好像我们能大摇大摆的走进去\N{\fnArial\fs48}Like we could just waltz up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:54.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}一个无主的珍珠,一个融合体,\N{\fnArial\fs48}as an ownerless Pearl, a Fusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}和-和,你\N{\fnArial\fs48}and -- and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.05,0:01:00.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们只需要伪装,我就叫"艾斯呆板·宇宙老爹"\N{\fnArial\fs48}We just need disguises. I'll be Esteban Universedad.
Dialogue: 600,0:00:57.05,0:01:00.33,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}Esteban在西班牙语中相当于Stephan,而Universedad则是大学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:03.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文,你的名字并没有用\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, it doesn't matter what your name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:04.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们太显眼了\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're all going to stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.41,0:01:08.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不会\N{\fnArial\fs48}We won't stand out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:10.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}只要我们的表现与本来的身份一致的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}if we play the roles we were made for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:12.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}红宝石!蓝宝石!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ruby! Sapphire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:14.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好吧,各位,听她的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay everybody, hear her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:19.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}今天,我,作为蓝宝石,正在执行公务,伴随我的有红宝石护卫...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Today, I'm a Sapphire traveling with my Ruby guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:19.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嗯!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:22.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}还有我个人的珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs48}And my personal Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.09,0:01:22.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嗯-哼!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:26.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}艾斯呆板,我将你作为献给动物园的大礼\N{\fnArial\fs48}Esteban, I've brought you as an offering for the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}"可怜的艾斯呆板啊!"\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Pobrecito Esteban!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:30.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃,我呢?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:33.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你作为额外打手陪同我\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're accompanying me as extra muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:34.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}像她们那种?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Muscle like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:35.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}没错\N{\fnArial\fs48}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:39.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但我从没看见过其他紫晶\N{\fnArial\fs48}But I've never even seen another Amethyst before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:42.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那我做什么?如果我说错话了呢?\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do I do? What if I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:43.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}看着办吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just look the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你too young,我们长者\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're new and we're rusty,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.61,0:01:48.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们只用坚持到找到格雷格就行\N{\fnArial\fs48}but we just have to sell this long enough to find Greg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:50.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这真的管用吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is this really going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:51.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不\N{\fnArial\fs48}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:55.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们得呆在一起,直截了当\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just stick together, play it straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:57.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}让我们改变未来\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:03.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们永远不可能关住我的,你们这群石头蛋!\N{\fnArial\fs48}You'll never cage me, ya rock heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:12.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}说明来意\N{\fnArial\fs48}State your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:15.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我是来完成动物园的货运任务的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm here to make a delivery to the Human Zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:19.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}坏消息-人类动物园关闭了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Bad news -- the Human Zoo shut down,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:24.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}也就是意味着我们不得不把你直接扔进太空\N{\fnArial\fs48}which means we'll just have to throw you into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:28.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哈!看,他居然信了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ha! Look. It believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:33.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们在干吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:36.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}没什么,霍利蓝玛瑙\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nothing, Holly Blue Agate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}为什么你不告诉我\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why didn't you tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}蓝宝石来这里了?\N{\fnArial\fs48}there was a Sapphire here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你对她说了什么不敬的话吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}What have you miscreants been saying to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}没有,长官\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nothing, Holly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:50.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你一定要见谅啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}You'll have to forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:52.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}他们来自地球\N{\fnArial\fs48}They're from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}咳!道歉\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ahem! Apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:02:56.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}请原谅我们\N{\fnArial\fs48}Forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:58.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嗷!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:02:59.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}请原谅我们,璧下\N{\fnArial\fs48}Forgive us, Your Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:01.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}没必要再揪着旧事不放\N{\fnArial\fs48}No use dwelling on the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:04.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我为收藏集合带来了一个新的人类\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've brought a new human for the collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这多么新奇啊-\N{\fnArial\fs48}How unprecedented --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}一千年来什么都出现\N{\fnArial\fs48}nothing for millennia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:10.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}而现在突然两个人类接踵而至!\N{\fnArial\fs48}and then two humans back-to-back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:12.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}也许,这样最好吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, it's probably for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}第一个的状态...并不好\N{\fnArial\fs48}That first one wasn't in the...best condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸!那是他!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad! That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:17.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘘!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:21.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦,人类无尽无休的叫唤!他在叫唤什么啊?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, they're incessant barking! What is it saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}-另一个也很吵\N{\fnArial\fs48}- The other one was loud too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}而且还在不停挣扎\N{\fnArial\fs48}And all that thrashing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:30.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我很确定蓝钻石愿意亲自表达谢意\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sure Blue Diamond will want to thank you personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但你刚好错过她了\N{\fnArial\fs48}but you just missed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:36.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}紫晶,带这个人类去-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, take this human to the --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:36.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}等等!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:40.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}有件事,我们走了那么远\N{\fnArial\fs48}The thing is we've traveled so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如果就这么离开实在是可惜\N{\fnArial\fs48}and it would be a shame to leave so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:45.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}也许你能带我们参观一下设施?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Perhaps you'd grant us a tour of the facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:47.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我非常荣幸\N{\fnArial\fs48}I would be honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}来这里,伟大的璧下\N{\fnArial\fs48}Right this way, Your Grand Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}紫晶得留在这里看门\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethysts are to stay and guard the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃,但...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}大门\N{\fnArial\fs48}The door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:05.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你的珍珠总是与您肩并肩行走吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Does your Pearl always walk next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我在这就好\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll just be right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:11.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嗯,很贫嘛\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm. Chatty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:15.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}此设施原来属于粉钻石\N{\fnArial\fs48}This facility originally belonged to Pink Diamond
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}收留并任用本来毫无用处的石英们\N{\fnArial\fs48}and houses and staffs the otherwise useless Quartzes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那些石英制造于她的殖民地\N{\fnArial\fs48}she produced on what was her colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:24.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但蓝钻石与她值得信赖的玛瑙-\N{\fnArial\fs48}But Blue Diamond and her trusted Agate --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}也就是我-\N{\fnArial\fs48}that's me --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:28.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}自第二代的曙光后一直在维护这个地方\N{\fnArial\fs48}have been maintaining this place since the dawn of Era 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:36.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}是她要做什么,还是我要先说什么?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is she going to do it, or should I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:36.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:38.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}珍珠,门\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl, the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嗯?噢!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hm? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好,好\N{\fnArial\fs48}Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:42.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我知道了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你对她真是有耐心啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}You are so patient with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:48.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你是如何做到的?\N{\fnArial\fs48}How do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:51.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}作为蓝宝石,我知道这肯定会发生的\N{\fnArial\fs48}As a Sapphire, I know it will happen eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:58.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}就这样吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}That will be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:04:59.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对不起\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}坚持一下\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:03.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}跟上啊,珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs48}Do keep up, Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这个设施的下半部分\N{\fnArial\fs48}The bottom half of this structure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:12.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}完全关注于物种保存\N{\fnArial\fs48}is devoted entirely to specimen containment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}显然,人类不愿意被拘禁\N{\fnArial\fs48}Apparently, humans don't take well to captivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:18.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但只要你了解他们的需求\N{\fnArial\fs48}But once you understand their needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}他们很容易控制\N{\fnArial\fs48}they're easy to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:23.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这真是个悲剧-粉钻在宇宙中的存在\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's tragic that Pink Diamond's existence in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}居然如此有限\N{\fnArial\fs48}ended up being so finite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但蓝钻的表现是如此无私,\N{\fnArial\fs48}But what a selfless act for Blue Diamond
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:31.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}愿意站出来花费自己的时间与精力\N{\fnArial\fs48}to step forward and spend her own time and energy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:34.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}保存这个地方-只为纪念粉钻石\N{\fnArial\fs48}preserving this place in Pink Diamond's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:38.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这是蓝钻石仁慈与友爱\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's a real testament to Blue Diamond's merciful
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}真正的纪念碑,你不觉得吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}and giving nature, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃,当然\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:46.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}坚持住,红宝石,我们的角色,记得吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hold it together, Ruby. Our roles, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63\pos(960,120)\c&HFABDA0&}然后走这里,是健康保留分区\N{\fnArial\fs48}And pass this way, the health reservation sector,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:48.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}一定要"艾斯呆板"住啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Gotta Esteban it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:51.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}而这里,显然,是人类处理滑槽\N{\fnArial\fs48}And here, of course, is the human disposal chute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}什-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如-如何进入动物园?\N{\fnArial\fs48}H-How do get in the zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:57.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦,又是那滑稽的噪音\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, there it goes again with its hilarious noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那么,你是如何进入动物园的?\N{\fnArial\fs48}So, how do you get in the zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:02.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}非常好的问题,伟大的壁下\N{\fnArial\fs48}Excellent question, Your Grand Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:04.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}在一些特别情况下\N{\fnArial\fs48}On the rare occasion that we would need
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们进入收容区域\N{\fnArial\fs48}to enter the containment area,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}要通过这个维护大门\N{\fnArial\fs48}we would do so via this service door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:11.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸,这个门是我们找到爸爸的关键\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad. That door's how we get to Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们只需要分散一下注意力\N{\fnArial\fs48}We just need to come up with a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:13.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好的!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:17.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}作为单向接入点,这里并没有发生逃脱的可能性\N{\fnArial\fs48}As one-way access point, there are no risks of an escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}实际上,只有一次这里被用于一个人类-\N{\fnArial\fs48}In fact, it's only been used once for a human --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:20.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爆炸!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:22.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对不起?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:23.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:26.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我刚想起来我忘了关掉引力引擎了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just remembered I left the gravity engine idling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:31.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对不起,蓝宝石,我真是健忘和廉价啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry, my Sapphire, I'm so forgetful and disposable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:32.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这?\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:37.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}...是一个我预见到的事件\N{\fnArial\fs48}...a foreseen turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}是的,它将会过热并爆炸\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, it is going to overheat and explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}破坏会非常巨大\N{\fnArial\fs48}The damage will be massive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:43.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我的言辞啊!\N{\fnArial\fs48}My word!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:46.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我不知道为什么有人会将宇宙飞船托付给红宝石\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know why anyone trusts Rubies with those ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:48.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这就是后果\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:50.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如果我们抓紧,我们能关掉引擎\N{\fnArial\fs48}If we hurry, we can disable the engine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}避免任何破坏\N{\fnArial\fs48}before any damage is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我应该只要五分钟\N{\fnArial\fs48}I should only take five minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:57.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}所以每个人要做到行为规矩\N{\fnArial\fs48}so everyone be on your best behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:06:59.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嗯?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:01.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}噢!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:03.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}来这里,璧下\N{\fnArial\fs48}This way, Your Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}虽然,我确定你不需要我的指引\N{\fnArial\fs48}Although, I'm sure you don't need my guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:08.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}啊!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我才不信\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't believe all that stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}蓝宝石有那么仁慈!\N{\fnArial\fs48}about Blue Diamond being merciful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}她会粉碎宝石啊!\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's a shatterer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:17.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}她对蓝宝石大喊大叫!她憎恨融合!\N{\fnArial\fs48}She yelled at Sapphire! She hates Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}还有爱!\N{\fnArial\fs48}And love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:21.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我知道,红宝石,但我们并没有多少时间了!\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know, Ruby, but we don't have much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:22.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们得打开这道门!\N{\fnArial\fs48}We have to open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:23.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好,好\N{\fnArial\fs48}Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:25.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}珍珠,开门!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl, open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}当然,我还会做什么?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Of course. What else am I good for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这个和其他的不一样\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's different than the other ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}啊哈!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:43.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我其实根本理解不了这个\N{\fnArial\fs48}I actually can't figure this out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}什么?!\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:46.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但珍珠,你是团队里的骇客\N{\fnArial\fs48}But Pearl, you're our hacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们没那么多时间!\N{\fnArial\fs48}We don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文,帮我打开门!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, help me open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:50.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}还有,珍珠,骇得快点!\N{\fnArial\fs48}And Pearl, hack faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:02.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我很高兴我们马上就回来了!\N{\fnArial\fs48}I am so glad we're almost back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:05.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我真的很享受这次行程!\N{\fnArial\fs48}I was really enjoying the tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}使得,我能从你的声音里听出来\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, I can tell by the tone of your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:12.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}再次感谢你避免了这次危机\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thank you so much again for averting that crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}发生了什么?\N{\fnArial\fs48}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:19.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦,呃,我确定这有合理的解释-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, well, I'm sure there's a reasonable --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:21.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们看到是哪个紫晶做的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Did you see the Amethyst that did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:25.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们可是有客人\N{\fnArial\fs48}Really, we have guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:27.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}霍利蓝玛瑙-我们有非常重要的消息给你!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Holly Blue Agate, - We have important news for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:31.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们在这些走廊中不能跑动或喧哗!\N{\fnArial\fs48}We do not run or shout in these hallways!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我对不起,只-只是-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sorry, i-it's just that --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:35.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我怎么听出来你要说什么,\N{\fnArial\fs48}How am I supposed to know what you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:36.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}像你这样含混的话?\N{\fnArial\fs48}when you're mumbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃,对不起,霍利蓝玛瑙,只是-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, I'm sorry, Holly Blue Agate, it's just --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:41.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}蓝钻石要来这里!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Blue Diamond is on her way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:43.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦 ,我的星星啊!她这就回来了?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, my stars! She's back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们两个,注意举止!\N{\fnArial\fs48}You two, best behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}肩膀要平!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Shoulders squared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:49.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}头脑专注!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Minds cleared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:51.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}站直了!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Backs straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}而且,蓝钻石\N{\fnArial\fs48}And surely, Blue Diamond
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:55.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}肯定想亲自对您表达谢意\N{\fnArial\fs48}will want to thank you personally
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}非常感谢您的特别货物,伟大的璧下\N{\fnArial\fs48}for this special delivery, Your Grand Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:01.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}是的,我觉得她会的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, I suppose she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:06.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那么别傻站在这里,你们这群没用的土包子,\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well don't just stand there, you useless chunks of earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}做点实事,护送那个人类\N{\fnArial\fs48}make yourself useful and escort that human
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:10.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}到同化隔间!\N{\fnArial\fs48}to the assimilation bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:12.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但是行程\N{\fnArial\fs48}But the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:15.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦,璧下,您真是太抬举我了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, Your Clarity, you flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但我们真的必须得做好准备了\N{\fnArial\fs48}But we really must get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们的钻石随时都会到达!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Our Diamond will be here at any moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:22.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}放开我,你们这群大号的紫晶!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let me go, you bigger Amethyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:25.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哈,这些新鲜的人类真是胆肥啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ha. These newer humans are so spunky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}进去吧!\N{\fnArial\fs48}In you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:49.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这是-\N{\fnArial\fs48}What the --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:02.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘿!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:07.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我自己会脱\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can do that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}看样子只能光着身子找爸爸了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll just find my dad without pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}兜裆布\N{\fnArial\fs48}Loin cloths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:37.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好吧,还有什么?你们还想从我这里得到什么?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, what else, huh? What else you got for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我现在处于老爸任务的肾上腺素模式\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm on that dad-mission adrenalin rush
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}随时准备着对付你们接下来的太空狗屁呢\N{\fnArial\fs48}and ready for whatever space junk you have next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}高科技赶牛棒,人用马掌-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Futuristic cattle prods, human horseshoes --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}随便你,来对付我啊!\N{\fnArial\fs48}whatever you got, come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:01.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:02.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}什么-\N{\fnArial\fs48}What the --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这是哪里?\N{\fnArial\fs48}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:08.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}而-而且爸爸在...\N{\fnArial\fs48}A-And where's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:11.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这儿?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad?
